<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Demand Promissory Note - Satin Finserv Limited</title>
  <style>
    /* A4 Dimensions and Page breaks for PDF engines */
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      width: 210mm;
      min-height: 297mm;
      padding: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      page-break-after: always;
      overflow: hidden;
      color: #000000;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .page:last-child {
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    .doc-title {
      font-size: 12pt;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .revenue-stamp {
      width: 90px;
      height: 90px;
      border: 1px solid #000000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin: 0 auto 30px auto;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .amount-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 11pt;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .body-text {
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: justify;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .signed-block {
      margin-top: 45px;
      font-size: 11pt;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .signed-block .signed-by {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .signed-block .signed-name {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .sign-img {
      height: 55px;
      width: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 4px 0;
    }

    .page-footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 12mm;
      right: 20mm;
      font-size: 9pt;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%
    // Safely assign variables or fallbacks
    const safeLoanAmount = typeof loanAmount !== 'undefined' ? loanAmount : '__________';
    const safeAmountInWords = typeof amountInWords !== 'undefined' ? amountInWords : '__________';
    const safeBorrowerName = typeof borrowerName !== 'undefined' ? borrowerName : '__________';
    const safeBorrowerAddress = typeof borrowerAddress !== 'undefined' ? borrowerAddress : '__________';
    const safeRoi = typeof roi !== 'undefined' ? roi : '____';
    const safePlace = typeof place !== 'undefined' ? place : 'Delhi';
    const safeRests = typeof rests !== 'undefined' ? rests : 'monthly/quarterly/annual';
  %>

  <!-- ================= PAGE 1 ================= -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="doc-title">Demand Promissory Note</div>

    <div class="revenue-stamp">Revenue<br>Stamp</div>

    <div class="amount-row">
      <div>INR <b><%= safeLoanAmount %></b></div>
      <div>Place: <%= safePlace %></div>
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
      ON DEMAND I, <b><%= safeBorrowerName %></b>, an Indian inhabitant, residing at <b><%= safeBorrowerAddress %></b>. (the
      "Borrower"), promise to pay to SFL (Legal Entity name &ndash; Satin Finserv Limited), a company incorporated under the
      laws of India having its registered office at 4th Floor, &lsquo;B&rsquo; Wing, Plot No. 492, Udyog Vihar, Phase -III
      Gurugram, Haryana &ndash; 122016 (the "Lender" including, its successors and assigns), the sum of INR
      <b><%= safeLoanAmount %></b>/- (Indian Rupees <b><%= safeAmountInWords %></b> Only) together with interest from the date
      hereof, at the rate of <b><%= safeRoi %></b>% per annum (pursuant to the terms of the facility agreement dated executed
      date of affixing of the last Digital Signature Certificate, payable with [<%= safeRests %>] rests, for value received.
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
      The DPN shall operate as continuing security to you to be enforceable for the repayment of the ultimate balance and/or
      all sums remaining unpaid under the Facility now or hereafter, including all interest, Default Charges, costs and charged
      that become payable in respect of or under the Facility or which may in future be advanced to us by you and we will remain
      liable under the DPN notwithstanding payment made in connection with the Facility from time to time or the amounts due
      under the Facility being reduced or extinguished from time to time
    </div>

    <div class="body-text">
      In witness whereof, this demand promissory note has been signed and delivered by the Borrower on the day and the year
      hereinafter mentioned.
    </div>

    <div class="signed-block">
      <div class="signed-by">Signed by</div>
      <img class="sign-img" src="/assets/sign.png" alt="Signature">
      <div class="signed-name">Mr./Ms. <%= safeBorrowerName %></div>
      <div>(Borrower)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="page-footer">Page <b>1</b> of 1</div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
